Positioning Elements by Floating
	floating elements produce flexible layouts
	Floats are taken out oif normla document flow
	To resume the flow use "clear"

Relative and Absolute Positioning 
	position:relative;  -> part of normal doc flow
	top:20px;
	left:20px;
	position:absolute  -> Removed from normal doc flow

